375
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:56,320
A sad sam već šest mjeseci stao.

376
00:32:57,040 --> 00:32:57,680
Ali ono.

377
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,680
Jel se dalje jede kruh i slatko?

